					<a href="../2007_08_30-the-best-idea-ever.html/trackback" rel="bookmark" title="Permalink to The Best Idea EVER.">The Best Idea EVER.</a>
				</h2>
			
				<p class="postmeta"> 

					Written by Ben on

					<span class="post-date">30 Aug, 2007</span>&nbsp;
					<span class="post-comment"><a href="../2007_08_30-the-best-idea-ever.html/trackback#respond" class="commentslink" title="Comment on The Best Idea EVER.">No Comment</a></span>
